, weak evidence)\n   - Tooling/infrastructure problems (sandbox, permissions, CLI issues)\n3. **Cost analysis** ã from the cost report:\n   - Total API-equivalent cost this sprint\n   - Cost per phase (which phases are most expensive?)\n   - Cost per story (which stories cost the most and why?)\n   - Wasted spend (no-op sessions, failed verifications, retries)\n   - Cost optimization opportunities\n4. **What went well** ã stories completed, bugs fixed, process improvements\n5. **What went wrong** ã failures, blockers, stuck stories, wasted iterations\n6. **Lessons learned** ã patterns to repeat or avoid\n7. **Action items** ã concrete next steps\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-04-03.md. If a session retro for today already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions ã proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":636,"cache_read_input_tokens":70581,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":636},"output_tokens":46,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"87203133-5cdd-4288-8e5c-bcff0e178735","uuid":"f98fc28b-f6ac-4647-9e5e-de564b0074a5"}
