{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015FsQ71XmHnxZufUHa3wDTG","type":"tool_result","content":"4270\t### Patterns to Repeat\n4271\t\n4272\t1. **Resolving architecture ambiguities at create-story time** ã the spinner vs `ã` decision was made early with clear rationale, avoiding dev-phase confusion.\n4273\t2. **UI component testing with ink-testing-library** ã `lastFrame()` based assertions worked cleanly for the WorkflowGraph component. This pattern should be reused for 14-2 and 14-3.\n4274\t3. **Single-story sessions have less overhead** ã no cross-story context pollution, no accumulated AGENTS.md drift, no format mismatch buildup.\n4275\t\n4276\t### Patterns to Avoid\n4277\t\n4278\t1. **Adding dead code props to new interfaces** ã `currentTask` was dead on arrival. New interfaces should only include props that have callers.\n4279\t2. **Deferring tooling fixes indefinitely** ã `codeharness stats --save` has been broken for 4+ sessions. The longer it stays broken, the less useful cost analysis becomes.\n4280\t\n4281\t---\n4282\t\n4283\t## 7. Action Items\n4284\t\n4285\t| # | Action | Priority | Owner |\n4286\t|---|--------|----------|-------|\n4287\t| 64 | Fix proof format template ã embed exact format spec with examples in verify skill prompt | HIGH | Tooling (carry-forward, no regression this session) |\n4288\t| 65 | Auto-generate AGENTS.md during dev-story phase, not verify | HIGH | Process (carry-forward, no regression this session) |\n4289\t| 66 | Fix `codeharness stats --save` to work without session-logs directory | MEDIUM | Tooling (carry-forward, 4+ sessions) |\n4290\t| 67 | Fix pre-existing `require-yield` lint error in workflow-engine.test.ts | LOW | Cleanup (carry-forward, 5+ sessions) |\n4291\t| 68 | Extract shared driver utilities (classifyError, parseLine) to common module | MEDIUM | Cleanup (carry-forward, 6+ sessions) |\n4292\t| 69 | Split workflow-engine.test.ts into smaller focused test files | MEDIUM | Cleanup |\n4293\t| 73 | Remove `currentTask` dead code prop from WorkflowGraph or wire it to a caller | LOW | Cleanup |\n4294\t| 74 | Add ANSI color testing capability or document the testing gap for TUI components | LOW | Tooling |\n4295\t| 75 | Continue Epic 14: stories 14-2 (task status driver labels) and 14-3 (activity display integration) | HIGH | Next sprint |\n4296\t\n4297\t### Priority Recommendations for Next Session\n4298\t\n4299\t1. **Stories 14-2 and 14-3** ã complete Epic 14 (Dashboard & Visualization).\n4300\t2. **Fix `codeharness stats --save` (#66)** ã 4 sessions deferred, cost analysis depends on it.\n4301\t3. **Fix `require-yield` lint (#67)** ã trivial fix, 5 sessions of noise.\n4302\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_0165HatmdNrNKJmxCFrwZHY1","session_id":"87203133-5cdd-4288-8e5c-bcff0e178735","uuid":"36c06e6a-0027-4747-8812-1dc0c87c67c3","timestamp":"2026-04-03T11:52:29.713Z"}
